ires|Pires]] 10\n|HT= 4\u201323\n|twomin1= 1\n|yellow1= 3\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 1\n|yellow2= 3\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Polideportivo de Almirante Brown]], [[Burzaco]]\n|attendance= \n|referee= \n|refnat= \n}}\n----\n{{handballbox \n|date= 19 June 2012\n|time= 16:00\n|team1= {{hb-rt|URU}}\n|score= 26 \u2013 13\n|team2= {{hb|MEX}}\n|report= [http://www.handballargentina.org/escuela/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Planilla-de-Juego-Uruguay-Mexico.jpg Report]\n|goals1= [[Jan Ansolabehere|Ansolabehere]], [[M\u00e1ximo Cancio|Cancio]] 4\n|goals2= [[Alan Figueroa|Figueroa]] 3\n|HT= 15\u20134\n|twomin1= 2\n|yellow1= 2\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 4\n|yellow2= 2\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Polideportivo de Almirante Brown]], [[Burzaco]]\n|attendance= \n|referee= \n|refnat= \n}}\n----\n{{handballbox \n|date= 20 June 2012\n|time= 15:00\n|team1= {{hb-rt|PAR}}\n|score= 16 \u2013 25\n|team2= {{hb|URU}}\n|report= [http://www.handballargentina.org/escuela/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Planilla-de-Juego-Paraguay-Uruguay.jpg Report]\n|goals1= [[Jos\u00e9 Mendoza (handballer)|Mendoza]] 7\n|goals2= [[Matias Gamis|Gamis]] 4\n|HT= 10\u201312\n|twomin1= 5\n|yellow1= 2\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 5\n|yellow2= 3\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Polideportivo de Almirante Brown]], [[Burzaco]]\n|attendance= \n|referee= \n|refnat= \n}}\n----\n{{handballbox \n|date= 20 June 2012\n|time= 17:00\n|team1= {{hb-rt|MEX}}\n|score= 12 \u2013 37\n|team2= {{hb|BRA}}\n|report= [http://www.handballargentina.org/escuela/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Planilla-de-Juego-Mexico-Brasil1.jpg Report]\n|goals1= [[Alan Figueroa|Figueroa]] 3\n|goals2= [[Lucas C\u00e2ndido (handballer)|C\u00e2ndido]] 8\n|HT= 8\u201314\n|twomin1= 5\n|yellow1= 3\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 2\n|yellow2= 3\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Polideportivo de Almirante Brown]], [[Burzaco]]\n|attendance= \n|referee= \n|refnat= \n}}\n----\n{{handballbox \n|date= 21 June 2012\n|time= 14:00\n|team1= {{hb-rt|MEX}}\n|score= 16 \u2013 22\n|team2= {{hb|PAR}}\n|report= [http://www.handballargentina.org/escuela/wp-cont