ise&sort=sumgross&order=DESC&p=.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=February 15, 2018}}</ref>{{Dead link|date=February 2020}}\n|-\n|}\n\n===Critical and public response===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  border=\"1\" style=\"width:99%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! '''Film'''\n! '''[[Rotten Tomatoes]]'''\n! '''[[Metacritic]]'''\n! '''[[CinemaScore]]'''\n|-\n| ''Despicable Me''\n| 81% (197 reviews)<ref name=\"RTDM1\">{{cite web|title=Despicable Me (2010)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1214097-despicable_me/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=November 9, 2017}}</ref>\n| 72 (35 reviews)<ref name=\"MCDM1\">{{cite web|title=Despicable Me|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/despicable-me|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=November 29, 2015}}</ref>\n| A<ref name=\"DMcs\">{{cite web | url=http://www.cinemascore.com/ | title=CinemaScore | work=cinemascore.com | accessdate=November 29, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Despicable Me 2''\n| 75% (181 reviews)<ref name=\"RTDM2\">{{cite web|title=Despicable Me 2 (2013)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/despicable_me_2/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=December 10, 2017}}</ref>\n| 62 (39 reviews)<ref name=\"MCDM2\">{{cite web|title=Despicable Me 2|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/despicable-me-2|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=November 29, 2015}}</ref>\n| A<ref name=\"DMcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Minions''\n| 55% (216 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|title=Minions (2015)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/minions/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=December 10, 2017}}</ref>\n| 56 (35 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|title=Minions|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/minions|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=November 29, 2015}}</ref>\n| A<ref>{{cite web|last1=Busch|first1=Anita|title=\u2018Minions\u2019 Is No. 2 Top Animated Opener With $115.7M \u2013 Box Office Final|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/minions-marching-to-114m-to-116m-weekend-box-office-friday-1201473955/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=November 29, 2015|date=July 13, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Despicable